com.marklogic.hub

Enum DatabaseKind

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DatabaseKind>
      • com.marklogic.hub.DatabaseKind
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DatabaseKind>

    public enum DatabaseKind
extends java.lang.Enum<DatabaseKind>
    Public enumeration for the types of databases in MarkLogic that the DHF uses. databaseNames are the string representations of types. Throws an error if an invalid DatabaseKind is specified.
